OL,3,CClimate scientist sheds light on
OL,4,Cextreme weather as report released
OL,6,FExtreme weather events in the Channel
OL,7,FIslands will become more likely due to
OL,8,Fclimate change, according to a UK
OL,9,Fclimate scientist.
OL,11,FIt comes as the UK Met Office
OL,12,Fpublishes a report into the state of
OL,13,FBritain's climate.
OL,15,FMike Kendon, a climate information
OL,16,Fscientist for the National Climate
OL,17,FInformation Centre, told ITV News:
OL,18,F"Our observations are telling us that
OL,19,Four climate is changing right now.
