OL,4,Cextreme weather as report released
OL,6,FIt is not only high temperatures which
OL,7,Fhappen as a result of climate change
OL,8,Fbut other extreme weather events
OL,9,Fincluding flooding and more aggressive
OL,10,Fstorms.
OL,12,FThe Howard Davis weather station
OL,13,Freported 2023 as Jersey's wettest ever
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FThe Channel Islands have seen examples
OL,17,Fof these extreme weather events in
OL,18,Frecent times.
