OL,3,CClimate scientist sheds light on
OL,4,Cextreme weather as report released
OL,6,FStorm Ciaran brought with it a tornado
OL,7,Fto Jersey in November 2023, leaving
OL,8,Fmany islanders displaced and in
OL,9,Ffinancial hardship.
OL,11,FThe storm also led to violent sea
OL,12,Fswells in Guernsey where more homes
OL,13,Fwere damaged.
OL,15,FJanuary 2023 saw Jersey hit with flash
OL,16,Ffloods at Les Grands Vaux, where 22
OL,17,Fhomes were left uninhabitable due to
OL,18,Fheavy rainfall.
